book.title: Tanner's Twelve Swingers (Evan Tanner #3)
book.description: Storyline: Tanner's Twelve Swingers (Evan Tanner #3) Out of print for fifteen years, Lawrence Block's third book in his hilarious Tanner series is back...And this time the intrepid spy is up to his neck in a dozen leggy beauties and a life-and-death smuggling assignment out of the cold corners of Russia.
book.author: Lawrence Block
